== How to update the firmware in TellStick and TellStick Duo using Mac OS X ==

Open the terminal.
Run the following command:
{{{
sudo launchctl unload /Library/LaunchDaemons/com.telldus.service.plist
}}}
You need to enter your password.

Now you can run the flasher utility, which can be downloaded here:[[BR]][http://download.telldus.com/TellStick/Software/TellStickNetFlasher/TellStickNetFlasher.dmg] (yes, despite its name it works for TellStick and TellStick Duo too)
[[BR]][[BR]]
